---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        line-height: 1.6;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
      }

      main {
        max-width: 960px;
        margin: 2rem auto;
        padding: 1rem;
      }

      .card-container {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
        gap: 1.5rem;
        margin-top: 1rem;
      }

      .card {
        background-color: #fff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
        transition: transform 0.2s ease;
      }

      .card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-4px);
      }

      .card h3 {
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      }

      .card p {
        margin: 0;
      }

      header h1 {
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      }

      header p {
        color: #555;
      }

      footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 2rem 1rem;
        color: #999;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <header>
        <h1>AI 公司对比</h1>
        <p>探索全球 AI 领导者的对抗，谁将在未来主导人工智能领域？</p>
      </header>

      <section>
        <h2>精选对抗</h2>
        <div class="card-container">
          <article class="card">
            <h3><a href="/compare/openai-vs-deepseek">OpenAI vs DeepSeek</a></h3>
            <p>从模型架构、市场影响力、开源策略等多维度，全面对比 OpenAI 与 DeepSeek，分析谁将主导 AI 的未来。</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
